    {
      "text": "High School Musical: Makin' the Cut! is a video game based on the 2006 television movie High School Musical available for the Nintendo DS. It was featured on Disney 365, airing on Disney Channel, hosted by Chester at the time.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "High School Musical: ¡Prepárate para el musical! es un videojuego para la consola Nintendo DS basado en las dos primeras películas de High School Musical.",
      "lang": "es",
      "source": "wikipedia_es"
    },
    {
      "text": "High School Musical: Making the Cut è un videogioco sviluppato dalla Artificial Mind and Movement e pubblicato dalla Buena Vista Games nel 2007 per la console Nintendo DS. Il gioco è tratto dal film High School Musical.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "『ハイスクールミュージカル：マッキン・ザ・カット！』は、2006年のテレビ映画『ハイスクールミュージカル』を原作とした、ニンテンドーDS用ビデオゲームです。当時、ディズニーチャンネルで放送されたディズニー365で、チェスターがホストを務めた回で取り上げられました。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
